    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/06/26/HUodbNi8uSXak3O.gif" alt="梦日记16周年"></p><h4 id="我一画梦日记相关就觉得我找到了初心（误"><a class="header-anchor" href="#我一画梦日记相关就觉得我找到了初心（误">☆</a>我一画梦日记相关就觉得我找到了初心（误</h4><a id="more"></a>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://i.loli.net/2020/06/26/HUodbNi8uSXak3O.gif&quot; alt=&quot;梦日记16周年&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;我一画梦日记相关就觉得我找到了初心（误&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;header-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#我一画梦日记相关就觉得我找到了初心（误&quot;&gt;☆&lt;/a&gt;我一画梦日记相关就觉得我找到了初心（误&lt;/h4&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    <category term="illust" scheme="https://tototofoo.github.io/blog/categories/illust/"/>
    
